{"tid":1300274,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實身在曹營嘅黃絲們有無機會建立黃絲區","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:11:42.000Z","uid":49898,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcc7c69db42f487b1a52735bcce21372095452a","tid":1300274,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"成日睇到好多巴絲嘅父母，屋企人都係深藍，相信大家每日都好難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />壓抑住就黎爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前有啲烈士都可能有機會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就忽發奇想，建立黃絲區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概諗到啲scenario係：<br />\n同熟悉嘅朋友或者戰友合租<br />\n咁在職嘅就出多啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />讀緊書嘅就少啲<br />\n但學生就多啲時間夾活動同出黎搞活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家又多啲時間傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋又有返讀書時候住宿舍嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就咁諗都覺得會幾有效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但現實一定好多問題：<br />\n性格，生活方式唔同好影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男女合租會唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有鬼混入就會冚家摌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更深入嘅就未諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11e2d51a004d36e91d4f72d9b46b73fa252525e","tid":1300274,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"41d00d48bfa6d41bf2be8e93f439bc9f522f00a4","tid":1300274,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"有無女女肯同我上下架床訓"},{"pid":"6b6b9d27a13301526e623b64dfd1bb199de376eb","tid":1300274,"uid":49898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41d00d48bfa6d41bf2be8e93f439bc9f522f00a4","tid":1300274,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"有無女女肯同我上下架床訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"咁分性別，安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e53d10d296a00c9dd7b59a804f8b26777fbaadb","tid":1300274,"uid":221927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"唔建議，有咩事一拉就成村拉哂"},{"pid":"430d18ba54bdb6742fadac1888a51d26cef6a5cc","tid":1300274,"uid":31778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"反抗基地易引鬼<br />\n小心"},{"pid":"d30ffd9c4fe5a79e340fc1717ca4b099088a2a89","tid":1300274,"uid":49898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"當我無講過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁應該搞多啲分區活動，等果班巴絲可以多啲見下識返啲正常人類"},{"pid":"58c7e5f977d368f8c2df85133d0d4198e1e242b0","tid":1300274,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:44:03.000Z","msg":"夾埋黎玩文宣仲好<br />\n有份做義士既一有鬼就連非義士都當你有份做鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c93c9573d5595013b40e81176f47a8e9f8a158","tid":1300274,"uid":83950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"開room party咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0a